{"analytics_identifier":"OT237","base_path":"/government/organisations/national-employment-savings-trust","content_id":"4d14dda6-55a5-4bfa-9e4b-25dda8207b37","description":"The National Employment Savings Trust (NEST) Corporation is the trustee of the NEST occupational pension scheme. The scheme, which is run on a not-for-profit basis, ensures that all employers have access to suitable, low-charge pension provision to meet their new duty to enrol all eligible workers into a workplace pension automatically. NEST Corporation is a public corporation of the Department for Work and Pensions .","details":{"acronym":"NEST Corporation","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The National Employment Savings Trust (NEST) Corporation is the trustee of the NEST occupational pension scheme. The scheme, which is run on a not-for-profit basis, ensures that all employers have access to suitable, low-charge pension provision to meet their new duty to enrol all eligible workers into a workplace pension automatically.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"National Employment Savings Trust (NEST) Corporation\">NEST Corporation</abbr> is a public corporation of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions\">Department for Work and Pensions</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-work-pensions","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"National Employment Savings Trust (NEST) Corporation"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.nestpensions.org.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"public_corporation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-08T16:35:22+00:00","links":{"ava